text: Eduardo Amorós (born 25 April 1943) is a Spanish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Spain Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
